{"tid":2204882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伊朗摔跤冠軍參與反政府示威     遭秘密處死","createTime":"2020-09-16T11:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T11:15:15.000Z","uid":192517,"like":23,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"8bb63dfa8cd438f851b42695334f74b83bf0feab","tid":2204882,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:17:20.000Z","msg":"27歲伊朗摔跤全國冠軍Navid Afkari ，被控參與前年反政府示威期間，謀殺一名男子。Navid Afkari在受到酷刑逼供、被失蹤和「電視認罪」後，被判謀殺罪成，近日更遭到當局秘密處決。 <br />\n<br />\n雖然事件引發國際關注，但Navid Afkari的例子在伊朗只是冰山一角。國際特赦組織今年9月曾公佈調查報告，指伊朗安全部隊對被拘留的示威者使用酷刑，包括︰水刑、毆打、鞭笞、電擊、性侵、模擬處決、拔指甲等，甚至有受訪者憶述曾被綑綁手腳，懸吊在橫桿上嚴刑逼供。<br />\n<br />\n了解更多 👉 <a href=\"http://amn.st/6181GQ6R9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famn.st%2F6181GQ6R9&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=9bd21884\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://amn.st/6181GQ6R9</a><br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織一直站在捍衛人權最前線，持續監察、紀錄、揭露濫權情況。我們會繼續與港人同行，關注 #香港人權 議題，合力堅守每個人發聲的自由與權利。<br />\n立即捐助我們&mdash;加入捍衛人權前線 👉 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZJO0sh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZJO0sh&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=c0d73d1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZJO0sh</a><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------<br />\n📢📢📢抗爭仍在進行中📢📢📢<br />\n香港示威跟進工作📍<a href=\"http://amn.st/61871Z4YV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famn.st%2F61871Z4YV&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=8a1d83b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://amn.st/61871Z4YV</a><br />\n人權學院🎓<a href=\"http://amn.st/61861tuz6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famn.st%2F61861tuz6&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=fbe40eb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://amn.st/61861tuz6</a><br />\n完成課程可獲國際特赦組織總會證書一張<br />\n為維持公正獨立，我們從不接受政商界資助，只靠你一樣熱心市民支持我們！<br />\n立即捐助我們&mdash;加入捍衛人權前線 👉<a href=\"http://amn.st/61821784e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famn.st%2F61821784e&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=3b6bfca3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://amn.st/61821784e</a><br />\n立即Follow AIHK Instagram👉 <a href=\"http://amn.st/6188146I6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famn.st%2F6188146I6&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=ad4a2749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://amn.st/6188146I6</a>"},{"pid":"d1584796e5e6d3b150d6ed3b792b912964531deb","tid":2204882,"uid":313615,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:21:06.000Z","msg":"伊朗政府好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30619c12d2c9afbce95c88faf54310ad2e8f1018","tid":2204882,"uid":155818,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:21:55.000Z","msg":"中東佬痴線架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7634d6dc8e302be0a811b2c18cad592232459c28","tid":2204882,"uid":25468,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:23:09.000Z","msg":"黑馬放一放生伊朗起碼延長左個極權10年命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2d1b6e82216749bd791ed0155387406b9a6e1b","tid":2204882,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8097163a1aed66c61b14cdba3bd66246ed15fa95","tid":2204882,"uid":192517,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"注意番伊朗支持匪安法<br />\n呢啲就叫蛇鼠一窩"},{"pid":"e07f19fed9da8a5094e53bbee9ccb069976ce1f6","tid":2204882,"uid":313615,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:28:23.000Z","msg":"阿夫卡裏喺伊朗全國摔跤錦標賽多次獲得獎牌。2018年8月，數百名示威者走上街頭，抗議伊朗日益惡化的經濟形勢和通貨膨脹。<br />\n<br />\n同時參加遊行有阿夫卡裏兩個兄弟瓦希德同哈比蔔，三人被捕後被指控犯有20多項罪名，包括參加非法集會、危害國家安全、侮辱最高領袖和進行反政府宣傳活動等等，阿夫卡裏還被指控謀殺了壹名便衣特工。<br />\n<br />\n最終，阿夫卡裏被判處兩項死刑和74次鞭刑，他的兄弟瓦希德和哈比蔔也分別被判處54年和27年監禁，除了監禁之外兩人都將受到74次鞭刑。<br />\n<br />\n但阿夫卡裏聲稱自己是在酷刑下被迫認罪的。據報道，阿夫卡裏喺壹封信 話喺大約50天時間，我忍受最可怕嘅身體同心理折磨。佢哋會用棍子同警棍打我，打我胳膊、腿、腹部同後背。仲塑料袋套喺我頭上，折磨我，直到我窒息。佢哋仲往我鼻子裏倒酒 水刑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n壹名法醫後來證實，阿夫卡裏喺監獄中所受嘅傷係酷刑，目擊者都話阿夫卡裏遭受酷刑情況。但伊朗最高法院駁回上訴。"},{"pid":"e9acd2437ae176434f8bcd393054eb3553415949","tid":2204882,"uid":313615,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7h7k2xv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7h7k2xv.jpg&h=915336b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zWC9bqR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzWC9bqR.jpg&h=280c0bd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90032d2a9753a2c7ac6ac1d8b9afb2a16c09f590","tid":2204882,"uid":246968,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:30:34.000Z","msg":"呢個世界就係邪可以勝正，好人總係受罪。"},{"pid":"de672f404094bd63bfa12eb023a06c7f634bdf9d","tid":2204882,"uid":199957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e9acd2437ae176434f8bcd393054eb3553415949","tid":2204882,"uid":313615,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7h7k2xv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7h7k2xv.jpg&h=915336b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zWC9bqR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzWC9bqR.jpg&h=280c0bd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:30:43.000Z","msg":"咁靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔係生喺個垃圾國 佢應該做到大明星"},{"pid":"1c1956ccc627205e146deb593bbe31844aa33a58","tid":2204882,"uid":273703,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:30:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8059628046e47b24f8673304708aee9e1e785aeb","tid":2204882,"uid":301820,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:31:48.000Z","msg":"我係Twitter見到佢哋reweet緊<br />\n<br />\n有沒手足